Component Control: They manufacture their own laser diodes and specialty optical fibers.
#Photonics

@stockplaymaker1 Lumibird is unique because of its vertical integration. They don't just assemble parts; they "forge" the core components:
Component Control: They manufacture their own laser diodes and specialty optical fibers.
$LBIRD #Photonics

@dontbuytops Photonics is the solution to scalability.

If we’re talking about mass production of photonics like EML/DFB stuff, there’s bottlenecks for sure.

Which is why I’m long the entire supply chain from substrates to foundries to osats .

